{
  "stem": "2713.5",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And when they saw each other, they kissed each other.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So they were very close together.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he said, don't worry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I will look after Maury.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Don't worry now, before even anything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He didn't tell him that he's going-- I am going to give him the diamond or anything.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But I then said to the boy-- I explained to him everything, and he gave me the diamond.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He gave me the diamond.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I put it in my pocket, and then I-- when we came there, I give him the diamond.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "What he did-- you see, those people who were cleaning the barracks had some-- something to do.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They were allowed to be in clothes, and they-- they had a separate bed to sleep for themselves.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And this is what happened to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "He gave me a bed next to his room, not far.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And he-- what he used to do at night, he used to, when no one saw, he used to come and put things into my bed to eat, and I ate.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So I got a bit of strength then, because he was doing it maybe every night.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then suddenly, he disappears.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And anybody I knew that came with me was nearly dead.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were-- they were all dying because it was impossible to survive there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And I couldn't understand.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said to myself, who knows now what will happen to me?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because I not getting any food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I had a better chance than the people did, because I was already in clothes So no one could take this away from me.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I was afraid if it takes too long, and if he's not there, you know, I don't know where I'm going to finish up.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
